content.task: Architecture review and technical guidance for Enterprise Features Phase 2 planning. Analyze the established Phase 1 foundation (enterprise module structure, security tier, configuration management) and provide architectural recommendations for Trading tier integration including liquidity management and yield farming capabilities.
content.context: Phase 1 Complete: Enterprise module structure with tiered architecture (security/trading/infrastructure), EnterpriseFeatureConfig framework, VaultKeyStore and HardwareWalletManager operational. Next phase requires integration of stellar_liquidity_management.py (1,147 lines) and stellar_yield_farming.py (1,116 lines) into the enterprise/trading/ tier following established patterns.
